{"tid":671140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於埋單 「新聞之花」張文采10月結婚","createTime":"2018-05-20T01:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T05:35:36.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ca48d189f7ac9f65d493fe4740a1b7f8461365a0","tid":671140,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"無綫「新聞之花」張文采在2015年與藝人羅鈞滿分手，表示開心能重生，原來她已升呢為準人妻，有指未婚夫是消防員，將於今年10月拉埋天窗。已拍婚照的張文采，將個人面書頭像轉為穿著婚紗的靚相，待嫁新娘幸福滿瀉。<br />\n<br />\n一眾新聞部新舊同事姚雋彥、李朗怡等，開心為張文采補祝33歲生日，姚雋彥在社交平台分享合照，為張文采送上祝福，「同準人妻慶祝最後嘅單身生日派對之餘，仲收到多一個好消息，呢個周末真係雙喜臨門！」李朗怡亦有貼相留言：「準人妻生日快樂 #五月壽星」。恭喜晒張文采覓得如意郎君！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180519/_2018051922520893630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180519%2F_2018051922520893630.jpg&h=943795e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/720235-娛樂-【羅鈞滿舊愛】「新聞之花」張文采10月結婚++\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F720235-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E3%80%90%E7%BE%85%E9%88%9E%E6%BB%BF%E8%88%8A%E6%84%9B%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B9%8B%E8%8A%B1%E3%80%8D%E5%BC%B5%E6%96%87%E9%87%8710%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%2B%2B&d=JJx%2BhOoRaLnw80yk8FS4fcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5978c83a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F720235-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E3%80%90%E7%BE%85%E9%88%9E%E6%BB%BF%E8%88%8A%E6%84%9B%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B9%8B%E8%8A%B1%E3%80%8D%E5%BC%B5%E6%96%87%E9%87%8710%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%2B%2B&h=e8017c3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/720235-娛樂-【羅鈞滿舊愛】「新聞之花」張文采10月結婚++</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多連登仔都想俾消防仔..."},{"pid":"cc3d5b3060bc19e3eb770c24d2ec552044b0cc43","tid":671140,"ui